


SHORT VS. LONG VOWEL

    BEFORE ACCENT

    ON ACCENT
        uenī ~ uēnī
        pedis ~ pēdis

    AFTER ACCENT
        caussa ~ caussā
        foris ~ forīs

    WITH ACCENT MOVE
        loquere ~ loquēre
        dūcere ~ dūcēre

SINGLE VZ. GEMINATED CONSONANT



GEMINATED CONSONANT VS. LONG VOWEL

    currō ~ cūrō
    palla ~ pāla